# Privacy Policy â€“ FlashLingo

**Effective Date:** July 28, 2024

FlashLingo respects your privacy. This app does not collect, store, or share any personal information.

## 1. No Data Collection

We do not collect any personal data. All your flashcards, learning progress, and settings are stored locally on your device.

## 2. No Internet Tracking

FlashLingo does not track your activity or connect to any external servers.

## 3. Your Data, Your Control

Since all data is stored on your device, you have full control. Deleting the app will remove all stored information.

## 4. No Third-Party Access

We do not share your data with any third parties. We do not use analytics tools or advertising trackers.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: **flashlingo.soporte@gmail.com**

